name: Cthulhumi
description:
cthulhumi is a monster looking to become cute

Created by :

Lazlo Barragan
Arthur Engel
Emmanuel Barbaut
Romain Saclier

GamePlay :

Arrow Key to move, Space to Jump, Shift to run

you can enter a new gamemode with Q, you control a tentacle

Arrow Key to move the tentacle, Space to drag or active an object, Shift to retract the tentacle. Retract the tentacle fully to return to normal mode
